bzh.plealog.bioinfo.ui.blast.core

Class BlastEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • bzh.plealog.bioinfo.ui.blast.core.BlastEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class BlastEntry
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This interface defines a BLAST entry. Such an entry wraps a Blast Result file, i.e. a SROutput object.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand

        public BlastEntry(String bClientName,
          String name,
          String path,
          SROutput result,
          DSequence query,
          String dbName,
          Boolean view)
        Create a BlastEntry.
        Parameters:
        bClientName - name of the client used to create this Blast result
        name - the name of this Blast result
        path - the absolute path where the file is located
        result - a Blast Result
        query - the query sequence
        dbName - name of the subject databank
        view - true if this is a simple view, false otherwise.
